OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start with patchy
OL,6,Flight rain in the west. Dry afternoon
OL,7,Fwith some hazy spells of sunshine
OL,8,Fdeveloping in the east. Brisk westerly
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIncreasingly cloudy this
OL,12,Fevening with the chance of a few spots
OL,13,Fof light rain. Later in the night,
OL,14,Fclearer spells and isolated showers
OL,15,Fdevelop, accompanied by freshening
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
